title: An Urgent Matter
author: Tigen
pages:
#- A lot of stuff happened last night, and I can fill you in on the details later. For now though, we need you to stay on your usual morning watch, specifically for our dear friend Folters. Josh fucked up during a pearl transfer and accidentally let him go.
#- If you see him online, you need to gather up any Chanadians you can and march on Kolima to catch him. If we don't pearl him again soon, he'll flee the area to his WP buddies, regear, and he'll be forever out of reach.§0
§0We're counting on you.§0
§0
§0-Tigen
#- PS: I did it. I pearled Rekvia.
#- 